Package xxl.core.relational.metaData

This package provides the classes that are needed for describing the metadata of the relational algebra operators.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColumnMetaData
    This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set.
    ExtendedColumnMetaData
    An object that provides information about a single columns of a given table.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppendedResultSetMetaData
    Appends a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to each other and returns a new ResultSetMetaData object.
    ColumnMetaDataResultSetMetaData
    This class provides relational metadata as specified by the ResultSetMetaData interface.
    ColumnMetaDatas
    This class provides static methods for dealing with instances implementing the interface column metadata.
    ColumnMetaInfo
    This class provides relational meta data for a column in a result set.
    DecoratorColumnMetaData
    This class provides a decorator for a result set's column metadata.
    MergedResultSetMetaData
    This abstract class is a ResultSetMetaData skeleton that wraps a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to a single one.
    ProjectedResultSetMetaData
    Makes a projection of a result set metadata object to certain columns.
    RenamedColumnMetaData
    Makes a renaming of a result set's column metadata.
    RenamedResultSetMetaData
    Makes a renaming of a result set metadata object's columns.
    ResultSetMetaDataColumnMetaData
    This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set by wrapping the result sets metadata.
    ResultSetMetaDatas
    This class provides static methods for dealing with instances implementing the interface result set metadata.
    StoredColumnMetaData
    This class provides relational metadata for a column in a result set.
    TupleMetaData
    An object that can be used to get and set information about the types and properties of the columns inside a tuple.
    UnifiedResultSetMetaData
    Appends a number of given ResultSetMetaData objects to each other and returns a new unified ResultSetMetaData object such that all column names are unique.
    WrappedResultSetMetaData
    This class provides an extended decorator for metadata of the type ResultSetMetaData.

Package xxl.core.relational.metaData Description

This package provides the classes that are needed for describing the metadata of the relational algebra operators. This package extends the functionality of the classes ResultSetMetaData.
